description:
Rockbot is the social & mobile jukebox app that lets you pick the music playing in bars, restaurants, and other public venues right from your phone. 

Start using Rockbot to:
- Pick songs to be played in the venue
- Vote on upcoming music to influence when it's played
- Share song plays on social media with photos and 'tagged' friends
- Discover and download songs that are currently playing
- Sync your favorite music from your iPod, Facebook, and Last.fm
- Link your favorite social networks to connect with users & businesses
- Unlock rewards, enter giveaways, and view current specials at the venue

Rockbot is available in hundreds of venues across the U.S. and is adding more locations every day. Follow 'Rockbot' on Facebook and @GetRockbot on Twitter to find out when businesses in your area are rocking!
